caption.p: Viral RNA level as genome equivalents (GE)/mL in circulation after challenge. GE levels in peripheral blood was measured by RT-qPCR following ZIKV challenge. Numbers of ZIKV GE/mL are shown 2 days after ZIKV challenge (a) and 4 days after ZIKV challenge (b). Bars indicate geometric means. The limit of detection of RNA level for the assay (100 GE/mL) is indicated by a dashed line. The * symbol indicates a p value of < 0.05, ** a p value of < 0.01, and *** a p value of < 0.001 as determined using the Student's t-test.
